    ('a1a1a1a1-0000-4000-8000-000000000001', 'Policy', 'Returns and Refunds Policy', 'Customers may withdraw from any purchase within 14 calendar days of delivery without giving a reason, in line with EU/Polish distance-selling consumer rights (odstapienie od umowy) -- simply notify support and send the item back in its original condition. For added flexibility, our Smart Returns program extends this window to 30 days on eligible orders and includes a free prepaid return label, so customers never pay for return shipping on those items. Once we receive the returned item, refunds are issued to the original payment method within 14 days, and most refunds actually process within 3 to 5 business days. Items that arrive damaged or are incorrect are refunded in full, including the original delivery cost, and never require the customer to cover return shipping.', '[0.0021635170560330153,-0.005902585573494434,-0.004805268254131079,-0.02764585055410862,-0.04874055087566376,-0.006957320496439934,-0.006564251612871885,-0.025719812139868736,0.0040191300213336945,-0.015473814681172371,0.011307284235954285,0.023440012708306313,-0.018749389797449112,-0.012394774705171585,0.0014175049727782607,0.007147304248064756,0.01581447385251522,0.003635887987911701,0.00017585742170922458,-0.007946544326841831,-0.012512695044279099,0.007035934366285801,-0.035769276320934296,0.019247276708483696,0.014268403872847557,-0.01724262535572052,0.02725278213620186,-0.0033525507897138596,0.021369850262999535,-0.04066953435540199,0.0054210759699344635,-0.010514594614505768,-0.02520882338285446,-0.015565531328320503,-0.0401192381978035,0.007782765664160252,-0.003796391189098358,-0.004428577143698931,0.003786564338952303,-0.019260378554463387,0.028589216992259026,0.028798852115869522,0.01453044917434454,0.0007906418177299201,0.007481412496417761,0.03980478271842003,-0.0030086154583841562,-0.007062138989567757,-0.002448491984978318,0.022483544424176216,0.02553638070821762,0.024632321670651436,-0.018133582547