    ('a1a1a1a1-0000-4000-8000-000000000002', 'Policy', 'Delivery Delay Policy', 'Every order shows an estimated delivery window at checkout, and most orders arrive on time through our courier and parcel-locker pickup-point network. If a package does not arrive by its guaranteed delivery date, the delivery fee is refunded automatically -- no request needed -- and the customer receives a proactive notification with an updated delivery estimate. For delays that stretch beyond 7 days past the original estimate, customers can also request a goodwill voucher on top of the automatic delivery-fee refund. Delays caused by circumstances outside our control, such as customs clearance, severe weather, or carrier disruptions, are still tracked end-to-end and communicated transparently, though they do not qualify for the automatic delivery-fee refund.', '[-0.005127040669322014,-0.027582310140132904,-0.017925754189491272,-0.01644224487245083,-0.023557601496577263,-0.01714279130101204,-0.013317256234586239,-0.020714204758405685,-0.011359846219420433,0.0059580812230706215,0.010151059366762638,0.015961477532982826,-0.031126253306865692,0.018969707190990448,-0.00680285831913352,-0.01642850786447525,0.018694981932640076,-0.0007194340578280389,0.002146282931789756,-0.015466973185539246,-0.01195050310343504,0.01704663783311844,-0.022966943681240082,-0.014024671167135239,-0.007184038404375315,0.011792536824941635,0.0334339365363121,-0.01143539510667324,0.03126361593604088,0.0014268489321693778,-0.0026322014164179564,-0.004951904062181711,-0.035741619765758514,-0.02559056133031845,-0.023516392335295677,-0.006795990280807018,-0.000594091136008501,-0.003911385778337717,0.016703231260180473,-0.012458743527531624,0.03255482017993927,0.018914762884378433,0.006679232232272625,0.005236930213868618,-0.008852987550199032,0.04414818063378334,-0.009745841845870018,-0.002685429295524955,-0.00968402810394764,0.018379049375653267,0.03368118777871132,0.01876366324722767,-0.013894177041947842,0.0023780814