    ('a1a1a1a1-0000-4000-8000-000000000003', 'Policy', 'Warranty Coverage', 'Two separate protections apply to every purchase. First, the statutory two-year warranty (rekojmia) under Polish and EU consumer law makes the seller responsible for any defect the product had at the time of delivery -- customers can request a repair, replacement, price reduction, or full refund, and during the first year any defect found is presumed by law to have existed at delivery. Second, many products also carry a voluntary manufacturer warranty (gwarancja), typically covering 12 to 24 months and registered directly with the manufacturer; this is separate from, and additional to, the statutory rekojmia, and its exact terms vary by brand. Warranty claims never require the original packaging, though including the order number speeds up processing. Damage from misuse, accidental drops, or exposure beyond a product''s stated water-resistance rating is not covered under either protection.', '[0.019312383607029915,0.011076219379901886,0.0033844003919512033,-0.03221435472369194,-0.03183567896485329,-0.006795849185436964,-0.0018578701419755816,-0.007242143619805574,-0.015025250613689423,-0.010528494603931904,0.0059674992226064205,0.02910381555557251,-0.016553470864892006,0.0023869997821748257,-0.011522513814270496,-0.004435897339135408,0.02047545462846756,0.020556598901748657,0.02223358303308487,-0.008831222541630268,-0.00746529083698988,0.023991713300347328,-0.04284427687525749,0.013598459772765636,0.010447350330650806,-0.007661390118300915,0.03213321045041084,-0.008188828825950623,0.02369418367743492,-0.00923694483935833,0.008635123260319233,-0.013889227993786335,-0.0456031896173954,-0.0050749103538692,-0.026209663599729538,0.006281934212893248,0.005325105506926775,0.003340447321534157,-0.0005980178248137236,-0.008209114894270897,0.030239837244153023,0.02569574862718582,0.013679604977369308,0.0034368063788861036,-0.0010371276875957847,0.014808865264058113,0.0027791978791356087,0.02358599193