    ('a1a1a1a1-0000-4000-8000-000000000004', 'Product', 'Wireless Noise-Cancelling Headphones - Product Description', 'Wireless Noise-Cancelling Headphones -- over-ear, Bluetooth 5.2. Active noise cancellation (ANC) with an ambient-sound pass-through mode for when you need to hear your surroundings. Up to 30 hours of playback on a full charge; a 10-minute quick charge adds about 3 hours of listening time. Stable Bluetooth 5.2 connection with a 10-meter range and multipoint pairing to two devices at once. Built-in microphone with call-noise suppression for hands-free calls. Foldable ear cups with a carrying pouch included for travel. Covered by the standard 2-year statutory warranty (rekojmia) plus a 12-month manufacturer warranty (gwarancja).', '[0.0011575353564694524,0.01022977102547884,-0.0009159990586340427,-0.012335900217294693,0.008177130483090878,0.004262404516339302,-0.015164130367338657,-0.032521311193704605,-0.010811463929712772,-0.0005516053061001003,0.021836882457137108,0.031906187534332275,-0.016875779256224632,-0.00738148158416152,-0.009026268497109413,-0.005957337096333504,0.01316497940570116,0.014655984938144684,0.014682729728519917,-0.009327144362032413,-0.044021446257829666,0.024899128824472427,-0.02610263042151928,-0.00784282386302948,0.0003217697376385331,0.0011558637488633394,0.01631414331495762,-0.01457575149834156,0.024350866675376892,-0.023200852796435356,0.028322424739599228,0.015337970107793808,-0.03225386515259743,-0.019082199782133102,-0.023053757846355438,0.0022381802555173635,0.001868771854788065,-0.016875779256224632,0.02595553547143936,-0.00021500069124158472,0.008932662196457386,0.008892545476555824,0.0062114098109304905,0.03075617365539074,-0.013579519465565681,0.023080501705408096,0.006816504057496786,0.008237306028604507,0.013445796445012093,0.010390237905085087,-0.005696578416973352,0.0031859383452683687,0.00796317495405674,-0.0026109316386282444,-0.015337970107793808,-0.021342109888792038,-0.027266016229987144,0.03832486644387245