    ('a1a1a1a1-0000-4000-8000-000000000005', 'Product', 'Smart Fitness Tracker - Product Description', 'Smart Fitness Tracker -- color touchscreen, 5ATM water resistance. Continuous heart-rate and sleep-quality monitoring with daily and weekly summaries in the companion app. Water resistant to 50 meters (5ATM), suitable for swimming, though diving is not recommended. Up to 7 days of battery life on a single charge. Companion mobile app over Bluetooth shows workout history, step count, and daily activity trends. Interchangeable strap compatible with most standard 22mm bands. Covered by the standard 2-year statutory warranty (rekojmia) plus a 12-month manufacturer warranty (gwarancja).', '[-0.010685895569622517,0.014957559294998646,0.00430535152554512,-0.030939240008592606,-0.007195798680186272,0.0057337312027812,-0.023662589490413666,-0.018878865987062454,-0.006808384321630001,-0.023231379687786102,0.000560908461920917,0.04258187860250473,-0.025117918848991394,-0.005292415618896484,-0.022436339408159256,-0.012242290191352367,0.020927106961607933,0.0071014720015227795,0.015496570616960526,-0.018029922619462013,-0.01069263368844986,0.016911474987864494,-0.014593726955354214,0.004800567869096994,-0.02576473169028759,0.0017349420813843608,0.017167504876852036,-0.021951228380203247,0.011548313312232494,-0.038000285625457764,0.023743441328406334,-0.013428115285933018,-0.04732517898082733,-0.0040964847430586815,-0.018622834235429764,0.010557880625128746,-0.013987339101731777,0.008967798203229904,0.016803672537207603,-0.008866732940077782,0.008859995752573013,0.022139882668852806,0.01336747594177723,0.0207115039229393,-0.025710832327604294,0.004376096650958061,0.014836281538009644,-0.0027540100272744894,-0.002041504718363285,0.027408717200160027,-0.007242962252348661,0.008678079582750797,-0.008637653663754463,-0.003319971729069948,0.009688725695014,-0.013960388489067554,0.02275974489748478,0.015051886439323425,0.011831294745206833,-0.02870234288275242,-0.0026377858594059944,